<div1 type="trialAccount" id="t17560225-20">
               <interp inst="t17560225-20" type="collection" value="BAILEY"></interp>
               <interp inst="t17560225-20" type="year" value="1756"></interp>
               <interp inst="t17560225-20" type="uri" value="sessionsPapers/17560225"></interp>
               <interp inst="t17560225-20" type="date" value="17560225"></interp>
               <join result="criminalCharge" id="t17560225-20-off102-c176" targOrder="Y" targets="t17560225-20-defend211 t17560225-20-off102 t17560225-20-verdict106"></join>
         
               <p>129. (M.) 
               
                  <persName id="t17560225-20-defend211" type="defendantName">
                     Mary 
                     Aldridge 
                  <interp inst="t17560225-20-defend211" type="surname" value="Aldridge"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17560225-20-defend211" type="given" value="Mary"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17560225-20-defend211" type="gender" value="female"></interp>
                  </persName>
               
            , <rs id="t17560225-20-deflabel101" type="occupation">spinster</rs>
                  <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t17560225-20-defend211 t17560225-20-deflabel101"></join>, was indicted for <rs id="t17560225-20-off102" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t17560225-20-off102" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17560225-20-off102" type="offenceSubcategory" value="grandLarceny"></interp>
               stealing a guinea and 2 shillings
            </rs>, the money of 
               
                  <persName id="t17560225-20-victim213" type="victimName">
                     Richard 
                     Perry 
                  <interp inst="t17560225-20-victim213" type="surname" value="Perry"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17560225-20-victim213" type="given" value="Richard"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17560225-20-victim213" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                     <join result="offenceVictim" targOrder="Y" targets="t17560225-20-off102 t17560225-20-victim213"></join>
                  </persName>
                
            , <rs id="t17560225-20-cd103" type="crimeDate">Feb. 16</rs>
                  <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17560225-20-off102 t17560225-20-cd103"></join>. ||</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t17560225-20-person214">
                  Richard 
                  Perry 
               <interp inst="t17560225-20-person214" type="surname" value="Perry"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17560225-20-person214" type="given" value="Richard"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17560225-20-person214" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I was coming home last Sunday was sev'n-night, about 12 o'clock at night, when I met with the prisoner in Holbourn; we went to a house of ill fame in <placeName id="t17560225-20-crimeloc104">Distaff-lane</placeName>
                  <interp inst="t17560225-20-crimeloc104" type="placeName" value="Distaff-lane"></interp>
                  <interp inst="t17560225-20-crimeloc104" type="type" value="crimeLocation"></interp>
                  <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t17560225-20-off102 t17560225-20-crimeloc104"></join>, and into a room; she insisted on my going up stairs with her: A woman came up for money for the room, I paid her, she went out, and I lock'd the door, and lay with the prisoner all night. I had put a guinea and 3 shillings in my coat pocket, and in the morning I missed all but one shilling. I challenged her with it, and she denied it. I saw the door was lock'd, and she came down in her shift, let me out at a back door, and I found my way home.</p>
               <p>Q. Did you not sleep in the night?</p>
               <p>Perry. I believe I did not sleep; I might be betwixt sleeping and waking.</p>
               <p>Q. How long was you in bed?</p>
               <p>Perry. About 3 hours.</p>
               <p>Q. What are you?</p>
               <p>Perry. I am an <rs id="t17560225-20-viclabel105" type="occupation">apprentice to a cooper</rs>
                  <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t17560225-20-victim213 t17560225-20-viclabel105"></join> in Lime-street.</p>
               <p>
                  <rs id="t17560225-20-verdict106" type="verdictDescription">
                     <interp inst="t17560225-20-verdict106" type="verdictCategory" value="notGuilty"></interp>
               Acquitted
            </rs>.</p>
            </div1>
